{"tid":1608084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"祝藍絲和支持藍絲的大陸人,將來被清算哂和逃亡好似林彪咁身亡","createTime":"2019-10-01T07:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T07:32:04.000Z","uid":267658,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d64cce9900f6a2bbfb0e56be8c5d4a467c1b284b","tid":1608084,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"對於班香港藍絲、何君堯等新界原居民等鄉黑、港共政權和支持藍絲,對香港反送中運動一無所知的中國人<br />\n<br />\n我只想講,由得你地<br />\n<br />\n不過,到時你地被捲入土地改革運動2.0、反右運動2.0、大躍進2.0、上山下鄉2.0、文化大革命2.0和其他等等的政治運動2.0,就唔好問點解<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>逃亡?????<br />\n祝你地好似林彪咁,逃逃下死咗</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然,毛澤東時代的土地改革運動、反右運動、大躍進、上山下鄉、文化大革命和其他等等的政治運動。<br />\n已經過咗好久、成為歷史和所謂的平反<br />\n<br />\n雖然,話就話「知錯能改」<br />\n但是,實際上中國由上至下,都沒有真正反省和反思過毛澤東時代的各種政治運動的錯誤<br />\n而且,重將它們復興,攪2.0版本,特別係維尼上台之後<br />\n<br />\n歷史永遠都係循環,人類總是重複同樣的錯誤<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.moegirl.org/common/1/16/Repetitive_error.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.moegirl.org%2Fcommon%2F1%2F16%2FRepetitive_error.jpg&h=80617dcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"969a18faa260415d04727946686175b251eea514","tid":1608084,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"祝何君堯等新界原居民等鄉黑,在土地改革運動2.0,被沒收土地和被清算<br />\n<img src=\"http://a1.att.hudong.com/23/25/300001062059133972258988245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa1.att.hudong.com%2F23%2F25%2F300001062059133972258988245.jpg&h=868c0e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://a0.att.hudong.com/68/58/50200009239445156200586771761.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa0.att.hudong.com%2F68%2F58%2F50200009239445156200586771761.jpg&h=3bdeb7e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/76/Choubapi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F7%2F76%2FChoubapi.jpg&h=99c0e8